io.apptik.comm.jus

Class RequestQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.apptik.comm.jus.RequestQueue

  • public class RequestQueue
extends java.lang.Object
    A request dispatch queue with a threadId pool of dispatchers.

    Calling add(Request) will enqueue the given Request for dispatch, resolving from either cache or network on a worker threadId, and then delivering a parsed response on the main threadId.
